 Anga\u017cuj si\u0119 w zbiorowe akcje, takie jak petycje czy kampanie, aby wymusi\u0107 lepsze traktowanie i wsparcie od Amazona.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3>Podsumowanie<\/h3>\n<p>Sprzeda\u017c na Amazonie mo\u017ce by\u0107 wyzwaniem, ale stosuj\u0105c powy\u017csze wskaz\u00f3wki, mo\u017cesz lepiej zarz\u0105dza\u0107 swoj\u0105 dzia\u0142alno\u015bci\u0105 i przygotowa\u0107 si\u0119 na ewentualne trudno\u015bci. Pami\u0119taj, \u017ce nie jeste\u015b sam w tej walce i warto korzysta\u0107 z do\u015bwiadcze\u0144 innych sprzedawc\u00f3w.<\/p>\n<p><b>Masz wi\u0119cej pyta\u0144? Skontaktuj si\u0119 z nami.<\/b><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<h2>Jak radzi\u0107 sobie z wyzwaniami sprzeda\u017cy na Amazonie?<\/h2>\n<p>Czy odczuwasz frustracj\u0119 z powodu wsp<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":7546,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[4],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-7545","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-marketplace"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7545"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=7545"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7545\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/7546"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=7545"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=7545"},{"ta